Package: jsfR
Type: Package
Title: R Wrapper for Python JSF Package via reticulate
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Nicole", "Wang", , "siyuan-nicole.wang@connect.polyu.hk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A basic R package that wraps the Python jsf package using reticulate.
    This package demonstrates the core requirements for the GSoC Medium Test:
    creating an R package that calls Python code via reticulate, with additional
    features including S7 object system and basic visualization.
